snippet.title: Dinosaur King Arcade Game 恐竜キング - Utahraptor VS Operation-Dinosaur Rescue
snippet.description:
Old gameplay, upload it because it is nostalgic. Next video will be back to the Alpha Fortress with Suchomimus.

Utahraptor ユタラプトル 猶他盜龍
Element : Wind 風
Strength : 1800
[http://dinosaurking.wikia.com/wiki/Utahraptor]

Moves / Ultimate Moves :
Tornado Toss トルネードブロー
Tail Smash テイルスマッシュ
Ninja Attack ニンジャアタック
______________________________________________________

Dinosaur King Operation: Dinosaur Rescue
恐竜キング アクト団恐竜捕獲作戦

These are my own gameplay video recorded using special emulator (demul) . I hope Dinosaur King fans will enjoy this video since this is one of our great childhood.
Special thanks to SEGA, the developer team and the ones who help me on the resources.
